                    "desc": "Here's where we store the actual vesting schedule.\n\nWe\u2019re using a Box because it lets us store larger or more complex data structures.\nAnd we\u2019re using a FixedArray with exactly 4 elements.\n\nThis is perfect for a \u201cstatic schedule\u201d \u2014 we know the number of vesting steps,\nand we never push/splice or resize the array.\n\nThis also lines up with one of the course\u2019s best practices:\n\u201cUse StaticArray / FixedArray when the size is known.\u201d"
